Requierment:
Linux or FreeBSD with Java, Hive and Hadoop on it.
Nginx && php 5.3+

To start Hive Thrift Server:
`$HIVE_HOME/bin/hive --service hiveserver 10000 &` 

Installation:
1: run git clone git://github.com/xianglei/phpHiveAdmin.git

2: add this follow to your nginx.conf in your "location ~ .php$ {};" area

fastcgi_connect_timeout 36000;
fastcgi_send_timeout 36000;
fastcgi_read_timeout 36000;

3: in php 5.3.x open $PHP_HOME/etc/php-fpm.conf modify to this:

process_control_timeout = 36000s

and this:

request_terminate_timeout = 36000s

open $PHP_HOME/lib/php.ini modify to this:

max_input_time = 36000

and this:

default_socket_timeout = 36000

4: restart nginx && php-fpm

5: open config.inc.php
set define('HOST','192.168.1.49'); and define('PORT','10000'); to your hive thrift server address and port.
find variables below in config.inc.php, change to your own path，and chmod etl,output_path,logs_path to 0777
$env['hadoop_home'] = '/opt/modules/hadoop/hadoop-0.20.203.0';
$env['hive_home'] = '/opt/modules/hive/hive-0.7.1';
$env['java_home'] = '/usr/java/jdk1.6.0_21';
$env['etl'] = './etl/';
$env['output_path'] = '/data2/tmp/phpHiveAdmin';
$env['logs_path'] = './logs/';

$env['lang_set'] = 'zh_CN.UTF-8';#system language set
#$env['lang_set'] = 'en_US.UTF-8';#if you are using with english
$env['setenv'] = 'export';
$env['seperator'] = "\t";#seperator(delimiter) set for hive external table

Open refresh.php
Modify
$env['output_path'] = '/data2/tmp/phpHiveAdmin';
to your own set , same as config.inc.php

Then?
No then, surfing in the data.

IMPORTANT:

for localized language using,modify /config.inc.php
 in this files, change "langs/lang_xx.php" to your language set.

accesslist intro:

[0]
;userset order above
username=yourname
password=yourpass
privdb=the database that this user can see
mrslots=map slots,reduce slots(not used in recent version, but future will be)

if you want to show all db, put "all" on "onlydb" area, else onlydb(s) use comma to seperate.



-------------------Chinese中文安装说明-----------------------------



系统要求:
包含Java, Hive 和 Hadoop 的 Linux 或 FreeBSD服务器.
Nginx 与 php 5.3+

启动Hive thrift服务:
`$HIVE_HOME/bin/hive --service hiveserver &`

安装步骤:
1: 运行 git clone git://github.com/xianglei/phpHiveAdmin.git

2: 将以下内容放入nginx.conf的php配置部分 "location ~ .php$ {};"

fastcgi_connect_timeout 36000;
fastcgi_send_timeout 36000;
fastcgi_read_timeout 36000;

3: php 5.3+以上版本 打开 $PHP_HOME/etc/php-fpm.conf 查找并修改如下:

process_control_timeout = 36000s

与这个:

request_terminate_timeout = 36000s

打开 $PHP_HOME/lib/php.ini 修改如下:

max_input_time = 36000

与这个:

default_socket_timeout = 36000

4: 重启 nginx && php-fpm

5: 打开 config.inc.php
找到 define('HOST','192.168.1.49'); and define('PORT','10000'); 并设置为你自己的hiveserver地址.
在config.inc.php中找到以下变量，并修改为你自己的路径，请赋予etl,output_path,logs_path 777权限
$env['hadoop_home'] = '/opt/modules/hadoop/hadoop-0.20.203.0';
$env['hive_home'] = '/opt/modules/hive/hive-0.7.1';
$env['java_home'] = '/usr/java/jdk1.6.0_21';
$env['etl'] = './etl/';
$env['output_path'] = '/data2/tmp/phpHiveAdmin';
$env['logs_path'] = './logs/';

$env['lang_set'] = 'zh_CN.UTF-8';#system language set
#$env['lang_set'] = 'en_US.UTF-8';#if you are using with english
$env['setenv'] = 'export';
$env['seperator'] = "\t";#hive中外部表数据的分隔符

打开refresh.php
修改
$env['output_path'] = '/data2/tmp/phpHiveAdmin';
为你自己的路径，与config.inc.php设置相同

然后?
就没有然后了，在数据里冲浪吧.

重要:

为本地化使用，修改config.inc.php中的如下部分
 将"langs/lang_xx.php" 修改成你自己的语言设置.

验证部分accesslist.ini设置.
[0]
;userset order above
username=yourname
password=yourpass
privdb=the database that this user can see
mrslots=map slots,reduce slots(最近版本不会使用，但是未来会开放)
onlydb写all为全部访问，写数据库名则访问单独的数据库，库名可写多个，以英文逗号分隔。